snippet.title: Amiga Longplay: MIG 29 Soviet Fighter
snippet.description:
An unplayable "After Burner" clone by Code Masters The creators of the famous Dizzy games).

This game is far so good as the Dizzy games. The game way too hard and i would say it's pretty much Impossible to complete without savestates!
